	- strrpos => mb_strrpos
	- strstr => mb_strstr
	- strtolower => mb_strtolower
	- strtoupper => mb_strtoupper
	- substr_count => mb_substr_count
	- substr => mb_substr
- DBEscapeString on $_REQUEST vars
- unescape strings for password encryption / to display / to search
